reviews.text: Food is reasonably good. Around Tsum Tsui Po area. Good pick for Asian and Western meal.
Good price for good Chinese food. Service is okay. Crew are attentive and polite. They accept only cash. The roasted duck with rice was delicious.
Nice food, reasonable price for the area

A range of meats and unfortunately they were out of the suckling pig. We got bbq and roast pork and it was cold and not that great. Came on a bowl of rice. I think your best bet would be to get here early in the day. The lady isn’t very friendly, yelling like service. Super cheap food though.
Beware of dual version menu, one for the locals and one for tourists. Horrible food.

reviews.text: Tried the 沙煲豆腐火腩鍋 since it's a must for guy when you are in HK.
Really good authentic food.  In a shopping mall.  Very busy with local folks
Don't miss it!  Delicious!

Found this place on the internet and went to have breakfast on 20 July 2018 with my son.  We are tourists.

Ordered two set breakfast from the menu.  The Continental Breakfast was $33.  My son ordered sausage (which was cold), with 2 hamburger steaks.  Beans with tomato sauce (again cold).

I ordered a set breakfast and was $30.  I asked the waitress if I want red bean drink, is it I have to pay $3 more and she said no.  In order to play safe, I asked her again and she said in a rather annoying manner "I have already told you twice and there is no extra charge" and so I ordered a red bean cold drink.  

When I asked for the bill, it came back with a total of $66.  I asked the same waitress to clarify the charges and this time she said an extra $3 for the red bean drink.

If only she has admitted she made an error, I am willing to pay the difference.  The other waiter then said how come I cannot read the menu which says there is a $3 extra charge on cold drink. I said I already clarified twice and instead of putting a $3 extra on my $30 bill, they just added the extra $3 onto my son's breakfast and made it $36!

This place has a bad smell, service was poor although the price you pay is cheap.

I will not recommend this place to anyone, especially tourists in that area.
0 star! bad taste, cold food (charsiu-duck rice) , nvm but bad cashier attitude! I swear no more next time!

24時間やっているので香港で深夜便でこちらに来た時には重宝させてもらっています。

また朝粥も安くて美味しいです。
安く済ませることができるのでちゃちゃっと済ませたい食事の時にはオススメですね！

result.name: 新源粉麵茶餐廳

reviews.text:
朝早くから空いているので朝食で使ってます。写真付きのメニューがあるので言葉がわからない人でも問題なく注文できます。
お粥や麺類など様々な料理が楽しめます。
金額はお粥も麺類も40香港ドルくらいからあります。
立地は尖沙咀にありアクセスはよいです。
味は問題ない美味しさ。
顧客はローカルが多い。

อาหารอร่อยนะ แต่โต๊ะแคบมากกกกมากี่คนก็จะยัดให้นั่งรวมกันโต๊ะเดียว มารยาทคนขายก็สไตล์ร้านlocalในฮ่องกง ซึ่งจริงๆเราก็ชินนะ แค่ร้านนี้ก็ออกจะดุไปหน่อย อาหารดีค่ะ ราคาก็มาตรฐานทั่วไปในฮ่องกงแต่ถ้าคาดหสังมารยาทและบริการที่ดี อย่าไปค่ะ

食過二次咖哩牛腩飯，都係$56。二次的質與量差天共地。
第一次，飯與餸分開上，咖哩牛腩內無其其他薯仔類其他嘢，全部係牛腩，分量十足！咖哩汁又多又香，好正。
今日再去食，咖哩牛腩淋係飯面，我一個女人仔都唔夠食。。。相差好大！下次都唔去了！

飯超級軟爛，份量特別少
店員態度超級差，懷疑的話
自己進去吃吃，便知真假

超級不推薦
路上還有其他好選擇

肉がとても柔らかい。美味しい。
変な日本語メニューが壁に貼ってある。
面白い。地元の人も多数利用。
早朝からオープンしている。
